---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';
import { getAffiliateCTA } from '../../config/affiliate-links';
---

<Layout title="Best AI Website Builders for Ecommerce (2025): Online Stores">
  <StructuredData type="WebPage" data={{ name: 'Best AI Website Builders for Ecommerce', description: 'Which AI builders can actually run an online store? 10Web + WooCommerce, Squarespace, Webflow compared. Features, pricing, limitations.', url: 'https://aiwebsitebuilders.com/categories/best-ai-website-builders-for-ecommerce' }} />

  <section class="bg-[#FFF8F0] py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">AI Builders for Ecommerce:<span class="block text-[#F5521A]">Real Online Stores</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mt-6">Most AI builders can't handle real ecommerce. Here's what actually works.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Quick Ranking</h2>
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-[3px] border-orange-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>10Web + WooCommerce:</strong> Full ecommerce, unlimited products, plugins for everything (8.8/10)</li>
          <li><strong>Squarespace:</strong> Built-in ecommerce, easy to use, limited scalability (8.2/10)</li>
          <li><strong>Webflow:</strong> Powerful ecommerce, expensive, designer-focused (8.6/10)</li>
          <li><strong>Wix:</strong> Basic ecommerce, fine for small stores (8.4/10)</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Top Picks for Ecommerce</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">10Web + WooCommerce</h3>
            <span class="bg-[#F5521A] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm">8.8/10</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Best Overall for Ecommerce</p>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4">WooCommerce powers 30% of all online stores. Unlimited products, 100+ payment gateways, 50,000+ extensions. 10Web adds AI generation.</p>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-4">Starting at $10/mo. WooCommerce is free. Most extensions paid.</div>
          {getAffiliateCTA('10web')}
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Squarespace</h3>
            <span class="bg-[#F5521A] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm">8.2/10</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Easiest Ecommerce</p>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4">Built-in ecommerce. No plugins needed. Inventory management, shipping, taxes included. Limited to 1,000 products on basic plan.</p>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-4">Starting at $23/mo. Commerce plans from $28/mo.</div>
          {getAffiliateCTA('squarespace')}
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Webflow Ecommerce</h3>
            <span class="bg-[#F5521A] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm">8.6/10</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Designer-Focused Ecommerce</p>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4">Beautiful checkout flows. Custom product pages. Full design control. Expensive and complex, but results are stunning.</p>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-4">Starting at $212/mo for ecommerce. Not for beginners.</div>
          {getAffiliateCTA('webflow')}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">What About Shopify?</h2>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-[3px] border-blue-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">ðŸ’¡ Important Note</p>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">Shopify doesn't have AI generation. You build manually or use themes.</p>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Shopify vs 10Web + WooCommerce</p>
        <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Shopify:</strong> Easier for beginners, more expensive ($29-299/mo), less flexible</li>
          <li><strong>10Web + WooCommerce:</strong> Steeper learning curve, more powerful, cheaper long-term, unlimited flexibility</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Ecommerce Reality Check</h2>
      <div class="bg-red-50 border-[3px] border-red-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-2">ðŸš¨ Most AI Builders CAN'T Do Real Ecommerce</p>
        <p class="text-sm">Durable, Framer, Dorik, Hostinger AI - fine for basic sites but terrible for serious online stores. Limited products, no inventory, poor checkout flows.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Ecommerce Features Comparison</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl border-[3px] border-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
            <tr><th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-bold">Feature</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">10Web</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Squarespace</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Webflow</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Wix</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Product Limit</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Unlimited</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">1K-10K</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Unlimited</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">100-50K</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Payment Gateways</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">100+</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">Stripe, PayPal</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">50+</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">80+</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Inventory Management</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">âœ“ Advanced</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">âœ“ Built-in</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">âœ“ Built-in</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">âœ“ Built-in</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Subscriptions</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">âœ“ Plugin</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">âœ“ Built-in</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">âœ“ Built-in</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">âœ“ App</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Transaction Fees</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">0%</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">0-3%</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">0%</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">0-2.9%</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Which Ecommerce Builder for You?</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Selling 10-100 products</p>
          <p class="text-sm">Squarespace is easiest. Built-in features, no plugins needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Selling 100+ products</p>
          <p class="text-sm">10Web + WooCommerce. Unlimited scalability, powerful plugins.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Complex products (variants, subscriptions)</p>
          <p class="text-sm">10Web + WooCommerce. Handles any product type with extensions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Design-focused brand</p>
          <p class="text-sm">Webflow. Expensive but beautiful. Full checkout customization.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Digital downloads only</p>
          <p class="text-sm">Any builder + Gumroad or SendOwl integration. Or WooCommerce with digital downloads plugin.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
